%e A349218 The 7-dragon curve starts as follows:
%e A349218          14    12
%e A349218           \   / \
%e A349218            \ /   \
%e A349218           10,13--8,11
%e A349218              \   / \
%e A349218               \ /   \
%e A349218          2---3,6,9---7
%e A349218           \   / \
%e A349218            \ /   \
%e A349218       0----1,4----5
%e A349218 - so a(0) = a(2) = a(10) = a(12) = a(13) = 0,
%e A349218      a(1) = a(3) = a(4) = a(6) = a(8) = a(9) = a(11) = 1,
%e A349218      a(5) = a(7) = 2,
%e A349218      a(14) = -1.
